What I really love about Kazi and Hamza's compositions so far in the season, is that the Rock and Folk never try to overpower each other. I have never heard such seamless and beautifully done transitions, from Keystation to a Harmonium, Electric Guitar to a Sarangi, Rabab and Dholak to Modern electric beats. 
Much Love!
